name: White Flag (for the Oceans)
description: Animated image of an 8 hour durational Performance Art piece by artist & environmental activist Carmen Danae Azor @carmendanae. Raising a white flag for the countless species we've already lost to extinction due to anthropogenic causes. 100% of the sale & royalties will go towards Ocean Conservation & Climate Action projects in the Dominican Republic where the performance took place. Video Duration: 30 seconds, Dimensions: 3824 × 2160
